trans-unit.source: Interacts with the parser to build the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Samhandler med parseren å bygge den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Adds literal content to the control.
trans-unit.target: Legger til litteral innhold i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The AppendLiteralString method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder> class overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AppendLiteralString%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class so that the method of the base class has no effect.
trans-unit.target: Metoden AppendLiteralString for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>klasse overstyringer den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AppendLiteralString%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasse slik at metoden basisklassen har ingen virkning.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AppendLiteralString%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The literal content to add to the control.
trans-unit.target: Litteralen innholdet å legge til i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the <xref:System.Type> for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control's specified child control.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref:System.Type>for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> kontrollen er angitt underordnet kontroll.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The GetChildControlType method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder> class overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetChildControlType for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>klassen overstyrer <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A>-metoden til <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: This implementation of the GetChildControlType method always returns `null`.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer alltid denne implementeringen av metoden GetChildControlType `null`.

trans-unit.source: The tag name of the child control.
trans-unit.target: Koden navnet på den underordnede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: An array of attributes contained in the child control.
trans-unit.target: En matrise med attributter i den underordnede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType*> method is overridden to always return <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType*>metoden overstyres for å returnere alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.GetChildControlType*>

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control needs to get its inner text.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> kontrollen skal hente teksten.

trans-unit.source: The NeedsTagInnerText method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder> class overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: Metoden NeedsTagInnerText for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>klasse overstyringer den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText%2A>metoden for den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klassen for å returnere alltid `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.XmlBuilder>

trans-unit.source: The inner text is the text between the opening and closing tags of the control.
trans-unit.target: Indre teksten er teksten mellom innledende og avsluttende koder i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText*> method is overridden to always return <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText*>metoden overstyres for å returnere alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.NeedsTagInnerText*>

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"></xref> control's inner text.
trans-unit.target: Angir den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml"> </xref> kontrollens teksten.

trans-unit.source: This method loads the <xref:System.String> passed in to an XML document to determine whether it is well-formed.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden laster inn den <xref:System.String>sendt til en XML-dokumentet til å fastsette om det er riktig formet.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: If it is, the code calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den, kaller koden <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A>-metoden til <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.SetTagInnerText%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value to insert as the inner text.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som skal sette inn som indre teksten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.String> object passed in is not well-formed XML.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.String>objektet som ble sendt i er ikke korrekt utformet XML.</xref:System.String>
